1
00:00:09,105 --> 00:00:09,764
<i>C'mon!</i>

2
00:00:16,479 --> 00:00:19,073
<i>Running like a fugitive,</i>

3
00:00:20,116 --> 00:00:22,277
<i>Being chased by something</i>

4
00:00:23,953 --> 00:00:26,615
<i>Inside my heart is pounding</i>

5
00:00:27,724 --> 00:00:30,352
<i>My throat dry like it's withering</i>

6
00:00:32,062 --> 00:00:35,156
<i>For no single one,</i>

7
00:00:35,665 --> 00:00:38,930
<i>To none does belong,</i>

8
00:00:40,403 --> 00:00:44,669
<i>This time is ours, right now...</i>

9
00:00:47,310 --> 00:00:49,175
<i>Unraveling the pain,</i>

10
00:00:49,279 --> 00:00:51,008
<i>Unraveling our hearts,</i>

11
00:00:51,081 --> 00:00:53,413
<i>Unraveling shadows</i>

12
00:00:54,951 --> 00:00:56,714
<i>Stifling our breath,</i>

13
00:00:56,786 --> 00:00:58,686
<i>Reaching for beyond,</i>

14
00:00:58,755 --> 00:01:01,189
<i>Tearing through the dark</i>

15
00:01:03,093 --> 00:01:09,657
<i>In fighting and in love</i>

16
00:01:10,633 --> 00:01:13,261
<i>To the distant light above,</i>

17
00:01:13,703 --> 00:01:16,900
<i>Yes, we are on the way</i>

18
00:01:21,611 --> 00:01:22,976
<i>I wanna rock...</i>

19
00:01:25,515 --> 00:01:27,039
<i>Rockin' my heart</i>

20
00:01:32,052 --> 00:01:33,815
He's late.

21
00:01:42,963 --> 00:01:43,793
Naruto!

22
00:01:43,864 --> 00:01:45,024
Stay still.

23
00:01:45,299 --> 00:01:50,396
Why's it that only
our squad's teacher is late?

24
00:01:50,738 --> 00:01:54,333
The other squads have gone off
somewhere with their new teachers,

25
00:01:54,575 --> 00:01:56,805
and Iruka Sensei's also left.

26
00:01:56,977 --> 00:01:58,137
Don't look at me.

27
00:01:59,980 --> 00:02:02,005
Hey, what're you doing, Naruto?!

28
00:02:06,387 --> 00:02:07,081
Hey!

29
00:02:08,188 --> 00:02:11,123
Lt'll be his fault because he's late.

30
00:02:15,729 --> 00:02:18,289
Man! You're asking for it!

31
00:02:18,966 --> 00:02:21,298
I like stuff like this!

32
00:02:22,703 --> 00:02:26,434
A Jonin wouldn't get caught
in such a weak booby trap.

33
00:02:26,707 --> 00:02:30,074
That's right. You're such an idiot!

34
00:02:38,085 --> 00:02:39,518
I got him, I got him...

35
00:02:41,522 --> 00:02:43,490
I-I'm sorry, sir.

36
00:02:43,757 --> 00:02:46,817
I tried to stop him,
but Naruto did it on his own...

37
00:02:47,394 --> 00:02:48,383
It's all good.

38
00:02:49,930 --> 00:02:52,763
<i>Get real.</i>
<i>Is he really a Jonin?</i>

39
00:02:59,039 --> 00:03:00,666
How can I put this?

40
00:03:00,741 --> 00:03:02,800
As for my first impression
of you guys?

41
00:03:03,243 --> 00:03:04,710
Well, I hate you.

42
00:03:10,217 --> 00:03:13,516
<i>Pass or Fail. Survival Test</i>

43
00:03:16,256 --> 00:03:17,086
Let's see.

44
00:03:17,524 --> 00:03:19,924
First off, let me have
you guys introduce yourselves.

45
00:03:20,394 --> 00:03:21,759
Introduce ourselves...

46
00:03:23,130 --> 00:03:24,290
What should we say?

47
00:03:25,065 --> 00:03:32,562
Your likes, dislikes, your future dream,
hobbies, things like that!

48
00:03:33,140 --> 00:03:38,737
Hey! Before that, please tell us
about yourself.

49
00:03:39,380 --> 00:03:43,680
Me? My name's Kakashi Hatake.

50
00:03:45,719 --> 00:03:48,586
I don't feel like telling you
guys about my likes and dislikes.

51
00:03:50,557 --> 00:03:53,287
I've never really thought
about my future dream...

52
00:03:55,863 --> 00:03:57,854
As for my hobbies, I have many.

53
00:03:58,499 --> 00:04:01,468
In the end,
isn't all we know his name?

54
00:04:01,802 --> 00:04:02,325
Yeah.

55
00:04:03,137 --> 00:04:04,536
Next is you guys.

56
00:04:05,839 --> 00:04:07,306
Let's start with you.

57
00:04:07,541 --> 00:04:10,009
My name's Naruto Uzumaki!

58
00:04:10,477 --> 00:04:11,944
I like instant ramen,

59
00:04:12,079 --> 00:04:15,173
but what I like even more
is the ramen from Ichiraku

60
00:04:15,249 --> 00:04:16,773
that Iruka Sensei treats me to.

61
00:04:17,184 --> 00:04:18,276
What I dislike is the three minutes

62
00:04:18,352 --> 00:04:20,286
after pouring hot water
in the instant ramen.

63
00:04:20,854 --> 00:04:22,947
My hobby is eating and
comparing ramen!

64
00:04:23,624 --> 00:04:25,558
And my future dream...

65
00:04:25,826 --> 00:04:27,316
is to surpass the Hokage!

66
00:04:28,028 --> 00:04:29,757
And so I'm going to get
the entire village

67
00:04:29,830 --> 00:04:32,958
to acknowledge my existence!

68
00:04:34,735 --> 00:04:35,667
<i>I see...</i>

69
00:04:36,203 --> 00:04:38,865
<i>this kid's grown up in</i>
<i>an interesting way.</i>

70
00:04:39,940 --> 00:04:41,840
Okay, next.

71
00:04:42,309 --> 00:04:43,606
I'm Sakura Haruno.

72
00:04:44,244 --> 00:04:48,203
What I like... I <i>mean, who</i> I like is...

73
00:04:50,784 --> 00:04:53,252
And, my hobby is,
I mean...

74
00:04:54,688 --> 00:04:56,417
My future dream is...

75
00:04:58,625 --> 00:05:01,753
And?
What about your dislikes?

76
00:05:02,463 --> 00:05:03,361
Naruto!

77
00:05:06,433 --> 00:05:08,401
<i>Girls at her age are probably</i>
<i>more interested in love</i>

78
00:05:08,469 --> 00:05:09,800
<i>than the Ninja Arts.</i>

79
00:05:10,237 --> 00:05:11,101
And lastly.

80
00:05:12,406 --> 00:05:14,374
My name's... Sasuke Uchiha.

81
00:05:15,142 --> 00:05:19,340
I have lots of dislikes,
but no likes in particular.

82
00:05:20,714 --> 00:05:21,271
Oh...

83
00:05:22,382 --> 00:05:23,007
And...

84
00:05:23,550 --> 00:05:25,882
I don't feel like summing up
my ambition as just a dream

85
00:05:25,986 --> 00:05:27,180
but I do have an ambition!

86
00:05:27,988 --> 00:05:31,856
The ambition to restore my clan
and without fail...

87
00:05:32,726 --> 00:05:34,387
to kill a certain man!

88
00:05:42,769 --> 00:05:43,701
<i>He doesn't...</i>

89
00:05:43,770 --> 00:05:45,601
<i>mean me, does he?</i>

90
00:05:45,873 --> 00:05:48,307
<i>Sure enough, Sasuke's cool.</i>

91
00:05:49,276 --> 00:05:50,243
<i>I knew</i> it...

92
00:05:51,645 --> 00:05:52,339
Good!

93
00:05:52,713 --> 00:05:54,874
The three of you are very distinctive
and interesting!

94
00:05:56,483 --> 00:05:58,178
We'll have a mission tomorrow!

95
00:05:58,519 --> 00:06:00,987
Yes, sir! What kind of mission?

96
00:06:01,655 --> 00:06:04,852
First, we'll do what we can do
with just four people.

97
00:06:05,492 --> 00:06:07,392
What what what?!

98
00:06:09,163 --> 00:06:10,721
A survival exercise.

99
00:06:11,498 --> 00:06:13,056
Survival exercise?

100
00:06:13,700 --> 00:06:14,860
Why are we doing an exercise

101
00:06:14,935 --> 00:06:16,664
even though this is supposed
to be a mission?

102
00:06:17,471 --> 00:06:20,235
We've had more than our share
of exercises in the Academy!

103
00:06:20,874 --> 00:06:22,364
This is no simple exercise.

104
00:06:23,110 --> 00:06:26,477
Then... then what kind of exercise is it?

105
00:06:34,755 --> 00:06:37,747
Hey! What's so funny, Sensei?

106
00:06:38,825 --> 00:06:43,057
Uh, well, if I tell you,
I know you'll grow disenchanted.

107
00:06:43,664 --> 00:06:44,289
What?

108
00:06:45,465 --> 00:06:47,695
Of the twenty seven graduates,

109
00:06:48,135 --> 00:06:51,263
only nine will be recognized
as junior ninjas.

110
00:06:52,072 --> 00:06:55,667
The remaining eighteen will
be sent back to the Academy.

111
00:06:56,210 --> 00:06:59,805
In other words, this exercise
is an extremely difficult test

112
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:02,508
with a failure rate of 66% or higher!

113
00:07:05,052 --> 00:07:05,882
See, see?

114
00:07:05,953 --> 00:07:07,250
You got disenchanted!

115
00:07:07,955 --> 00:07:09,252
That's crazy!

116
00:07:09,556 --> 00:07:10,887
To have suffered that much!

117
00:07:10,958 --> 00:07:14,450
T-Then, what was
the graduation test for?

118
00:07:15,229 --> 00:07:15,820
Oh, that.

119
00:07:16,363 --> 00:07:19,423
It was just to select those who have
the potential of becoming Genin.

120
00:07:19,666 --> 00:07:21,759
Whaaaat?!

121
00:07:22,202 --> 00:07:23,601
Well, that's the way it is.

122
00:07:23,937 --> 00:07:27,498
I'll be determining whether
you pass or fail.

123
00:07:28,108 --> 00:07:29,769
Bring your complete set
of Ninja tools!

124
00:07:30,010 --> 00:07:31,500
We meet at five in the morning.

125
00:07:34,915 --> 00:07:38,112
<i>N-No way am I going to be</i>
<i>dropped now!</i>

126
00:07:38,352 --> 00:07:42,049
<i>I've got to have my strength</i>
<i>recognized for real.</i>

127
00:07:42,823 --> 00:07:46,418
<i>I'll be separated from Sasuke</i>
<i>if I fail this test.</i>

128
00:07:47,060 --> 00:07:48,459
<i>This is an exercise of love!</i>

129
00:07:53,333 --> 00:07:55,130
Okay! You're dismissed.

130
00:07:56,203 --> 00:07:58,797
Oh... And you'd best skip breakfast.

131
00:07:59,373 --> 00:07:59,998
You'll throw up.

132
00:08:12,352 --> 00:08:13,751
Morning.

133
00:08:42,549 --> 00:08:44,642
Hi, folks. Good morning!

134
00:08:45,218 --> 00:08:47,413
You're late!

135
00:08:48,021 --> 00:08:51,752
Well, a black cat crossed
my path, you see.

136
00:08:54,528 --> 00:08:56,587
Ahem! Oh well...

137
00:08:59,066 --> 00:09:01,364
Okay, it's set for 12:00!

138
00:09:05,305 --> 00:09:09,901
Today's assignment is to take
these bells away from me by noon.

139
00:09:13,413 --> 00:09:15,643
Those who can't do it won't get lunch.

140
00:09:16,516 --> 00:09:18,416
They'll be tied to that...

141
00:09:18,485 --> 00:09:20,919
and I'll eat my lunch
before your very eyes.

142
00:09:22,422 --> 00:09:23,855
<i>So that was the point...</i>

143
00:09:24,658 --> 00:09:26,216
<i>for us not to eat breakfast...</i>

144
00:09:26,560 --> 00:09:27,857
But, hold on.

145
00:09:28,328 --> 00:09:29,852
Why are there only two bells?

146
00:09:31,565 --> 00:09:33,089
There are only two,
so at the very least,

147
00:09:33,166 --> 00:09:34,599
one will have to
go to the logs.

148
00:09:34,968 --> 00:09:37,732
That person will be disqualified
for failing the mission...

149
00:09:38,205 --> 00:09:39,672
and will return to the Academy.

150
00:09:40,707 --> 00:09:42,538
It might be one person
at the very least,

151
00:09:42,609 --> 00:09:44,201
or it could be all three of you.

152
00:09:45,112 --> 00:09:46,875
You can use your Shuriken.

153
00:09:47,347 --> 00:09:50,282
You won't be able to take the bells
unless you come with the intent to kill me.

154
00:09:52,052 --> 00:09:53,986
But, that's dangerous, sir!

155
00:09:54,287 --> 00:09:55,686
Y-Yeah, that's right!

156
00:09:55,822 --> 00:09:57,813
You couldn't even evade
a chalkboard eraser!

157
00:09:57,891 --> 00:09:59,153
In this world,

158
00:09:59,459 --> 00:10:01,950
those who aren't skilled enough
tend to complain more.

159
00:10:02,329 --> 00:10:04,456
Well, just ignore the loser...

160
00:10:06,199 --> 00:10:07,928
Begin when I give
the "ready-go" signal.

161
00:10:08,001 --> 00:10:09,935
<i>Loser, loser, loser.</i>

162
00:10:25,685 --> 00:10:29,678
Don't be so hasty.
I didn't say start, yet.

163
00:10:37,531 --> 00:10:38,225
<i>No way...!</i>

164
00:10:38,698 --> 00:10:39,995
<i>I didn't see him at all.</i>

165
00:10:40,967 --> 00:10:42,298
<i>So this is a Jonin.</i>

166
00:10:43,170 --> 00:10:44,034
But, that's fine.

167
00:10:44,104 --> 00:10:47,369
At least you came with
the intent to kill me.

168
00:10:49,543 --> 00:10:50,737
How can I put this?

169
00:10:50,977 --> 00:10:52,069
I feel like I'm finally starting...

170
00:10:52,145 --> 00:10:53,339
to like you guys.

171
00:10:54,848 --> 00:10:55,780
We're going to start.

172
00:10:56,850 --> 00:10:59,250
Ready... start!

173
00:11:03,312 --> 00:11:04,870
What do you want to know?

174
00:11:06,716 --> 00:11:10,174
I didn't think you just
came here to drink tea.

175
00:11:11,020 --> 00:11:13,454
The Jonin in Naruto and company's
Group Seven...

176
00:11:14,157 --> 00:11:17,718
What kind of teacher is he?
Is he strict?

177
00:11:19,028 --> 00:11:22,259
You mean Kakashi?
Does he concern you?

178
00:11:23,599 --> 00:11:26,534
I heard a rumor that concerns me.

179
00:11:34,210 --> 00:11:34,835
What's this?

180
00:11:36,212 --> 00:11:38,544
It's a pass fail list of
the junior ninjas

181
00:11:38,614 --> 00:11:40,673
Kakashi has been
in charge of up until now.

182
00:11:43,186 --> 00:11:44,084
Let me have a look.

183
00:11:50,460 --> 00:11:52,052
T-This is!

184
00:11:55,832 --> 00:11:59,324
Fundamentally, ninja must mask
their presence and hide.

185
00:12:08,110 --> 00:12:10,670
Okay, everyone is hidden pretty well...

186
00:12:13,850 --> 00:12:17,081
Alright! Let's face off
fair and square!

187
00:12:17,520 --> 00:12:18,077
Oh?

188
00:12:18,821 --> 00:12:20,083
That goof.

189
00:12:21,457 --> 00:12:24,153
Say, aren't you a bit
off kilter?

190
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:27,022
What's off kilter
is your hairstyle!

191
00:12:39,742 --> 00:12:42,734
I'll teach you the first
Shinobi Battle Jutsu...

192
00:12:43,246 --> 00:12:44,941
Taijutsu.

193
00:12:48,084 --> 00:12:48,982
<i>Taijutsu...?</i>

194
00:12:49,085 --> 00:12:50,950
<i>That's ninja hand to hand combat...</i>

195
00:12:51,254 --> 00:12:53,381
<i>That being said...</i>
<i>he's going to use weapons?</i>

196
00:12:55,458 --> 00:13:00,452
Make Out Paradise

197
00:13:03,199 --> 00:13:04,029
What's the matter?

198
00:13:04,333 --> 00:13:05,459
Why don't you come at me?

199
00:13:05,835 --> 00:13:09,327
But hey... what's with the book?

200
00:13:09,672 --> 00:13:10,900
Why do you ask?

201
00:13:11,374 --> 00:13:14,343
It's because I was curious
about what happens next.

202
00:13:14,844 --> 00:13:15,606
Don't worry.

203
00:13:16,279 --> 00:13:17,746
With you guys as opponents,

204
00:13:17,813 --> 00:13:19,212
it makes no difference
if I'm reading or not.

205
00:13:21,817 --> 00:13:23,785
I'm going to rip you apart!

206
00:13:27,323 --> 00:13:29,450
Damn! This time a spin kick!

207
00:13:31,027 --> 00:13:31,789
Man!

208
00:13:34,830 --> 00:13:35,626
Wha?!

209
00:13:36,432 --> 00:13:39,128
Ninja shouldn't let the enemy take them
from behind multiple times, fool.

210
00:13:40,603 --> 00:13:42,195
<i>The way his hands are positioned...</i>

211
00:13:42,872 --> 00:13:44,032
<i>Is that the Sign of the Tiger?!</i>

212
00:13:44,507 --> 00:13:45,064
<i>No way!</i>

213
00:13:45,174 --> 00:13:46,436
<i>With Naruto as his opponent,</i>

214
00:13:46,509 --> 00:13:48,340
<i>that's too strong a Ninjutsu</i>
<i>no matter how you look at it.</i>

215
00:13:49,011 --> 00:13:51,502
<i>That Sign...</i>
<i>It's a fire style skill.</i>

216
00:13:52,481 --> 00:13:55,075
<i>That idiot teacher's doing more</i>
<i>than just running around?</i>

217
00:13:55,618 --> 00:13:57,643
Naruto, get out of there quick!

218
00:13:57,720 --> 00:13:58,982
You'll die!

219
00:14:00,189 --> 00:14:00,985
Too late.

220
00:14:02,191 --> 00:14:04,386
Leaf Village Secret!
Ultimate Taijutsu!

221
00:14:09,065 --> 00:14:10,657
One Thousand Years of Death!

222
00:14:12,201 --> 00:14:15,068
Oh, it's not a Ninjutsu.

223
00:14:16,172 --> 00:14:18,470
Those two are idiots.

224
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:25,172
Alright...

225
00:14:32,855 --> 00:14:35,517
<i>Even so, isn't that against the rules?</i>

226
00:14:35,591 --> 00:14:38,355
<i>What're we supposed to do</i>
<i>about his strength?</i>

227
00:14:43,532 --> 00:14:44,726
<i>Damn it!</i>

228
00:14:44,800 --> 00:14:46,199
<i>It wasn't supposed to be</i>
<i>like this.</i>

229
00:14:58,914 --> 00:15:00,176
It... can't be!

230
00:15:00,249 --> 00:15:02,080
This is more than just a rumor.

231
00:15:03,185 --> 00:15:06,882
Kakashi's test might
be a bit difficult...

232
00:15:08,057 --> 00:15:11,993
Even so, this means absolutely
no one has passed!

233
00:15:12,628 --> 00:15:13,287
That's right...

234
00:15:13,496 --> 00:15:16,988
Kakashi has never had someone pass.

235
00:15:17,333 --> 00:15:18,163
They have all...

236
00:15:18,601 --> 00:15:19,932
been annihilated...

237
00:15:25,441 --> 00:15:26,999
What's the matter?

238
00:15:27,443 --> 00:15:30,640
You won't get lunch if you can't
take the bell by noon.

239
00:15:31,514 --> 00:15:33,709
I know that, I say.

240
00:15:33,983 --> 00:15:36,076
You're not very energetic,

241
00:15:36,152 --> 00:15:37,949
considering you said that
you'd surpass the Hokage.

242
00:15:39,455 --> 00:15:43,050
Damn it! Damn it!
I can fight even if I'm hungry.

243
00:15:46,395 --> 00:15:49,694
<i>I didn't even have dinner last night.</i>

244
00:15:50,833 --> 00:15:53,427
<i>I shouldn't have gone on a diet.</i>

245
00:15:54,170 --> 00:15:57,298
I just got a bit careless earlier!

246
00:15:57,840 --> 00:16:00,400
Damn! I'm hungry, so my strength...

247
00:16:01,143 --> 00:16:04,670
But... I've got to take the bell,
no matter what.

248
00:16:05,414 --> 00:16:06,847
No matter what...

249
00:16:07,349 --> 00:16:09,681
I'm... not...

250
00:16:10,352 --> 00:16:12,377
turning back now!

251
00:16:16,492 --> 00:16:17,891
I'm going to become a Ninja!

252
00:16:28,270 --> 00:16:29,794
Security is your greatest enemy!

253
00:16:29,905 --> 00:16:33,500
Now for my favorite
Multi Shadow Clone Jutsu!

254
00:16:34,376 --> 00:16:36,344
<i>Seven... Narutos?</i>

255
00:16:40,683 --> 00:16:42,810
<i>What? They're not just images?</i>

256
00:16:43,552 --> 00:16:45,918
<i>Are they all real?</i>
<i>The real thing?</i>

257
00:16:52,661 --> 00:16:55,630
Not the clone,
but the shadow clone, eh.

258
00:16:57,233 --> 00:17:01,829
<i>If you ever lay a hand on Iruka Sensei,</i>
<i>I'll kill you!</i>

259
00:17:01,904 --> 00:17:04,168
<i>Show me what you can do, Demon Fox!</i>

260
00:17:11,313 --> 00:17:15,613
<i>Those aren't just images</i>
<i>but actual clones!</i>

261
00:17:15,684 --> 00:17:16,878
<i>That's an advanced Ninjutsu!</i>

262
00:17:18,521 --> 00:17:21,979
<i>It's the forbidden Jutsu</i>
<i>that did in Mizuki.</i>

263
00:17:24,326 --> 00:17:26,260
Judging from your ability,

264
00:17:26,328 --> 00:17:28,728
that Jutsu should have
a one-minute limit.

265
00:17:29,632 --> 00:17:31,691
Even if you talk trash,

266
00:17:31,767 --> 00:17:33,860
Naruto is Naruto
after all is said and done...

267
00:17:34,503 --> 00:17:37,631
You still can't beat me with that skill.

268
00:17:40,309 --> 00:17:41,901
W-What?! Behind me?!

269
00:17:48,050 --> 00:17:51,451
Ninja shouldn't let
the enemy take them from behind.

270
00:17:51,520 --> 00:17:53,283
Right, Kakashi Sensei?

271
00:17:53,989 --> 00:17:55,320
Using the Shadow Clone,

272
00:17:55,391 --> 00:17:56,790
I had one of them come up

273
00:17:56,859 --> 00:17:59,919
from the bottom of the river
and sneak behind you!

274
00:18:00,696 --> 00:18:03,290
Here's one for that attack
on my butt earlier!

275
00:18:03,732 --> 00:18:05,359
<i>Naruto, not bad!</i>

276
00:18:06,035 --> 00:18:07,730
<i>So... a diversionary tactic, eh?</i>

277
00:18:10,172 --> 00:18:11,833
Now... allow me to punch you!

278
00:18:21,417 --> 00:18:22,384
What?!

279
00:18:29,191 --> 00:18:30,590
The one who got punched was...

280
00:18:33,262 --> 00:18:34,024
Naruto?

281
00:18:35,598 --> 00:18:36,929
Ouch!

282
00:18:37,266 --> 00:18:38,062
You!

283
00:18:38,701 --> 00:18:41,101
You're Kakashi Sensei, right?!

284
00:18:41,170 --> 00:18:43,468
You used the Transformation Jutsu
to change yourself, didn't you?!

285
00:18:43,539 --> 00:18:44,335
It's you!

286
00:18:44,406 --> 00:18:45,839
You're Kakashi Sensei, I say.

287
00:18:46,642 --> 00:18:48,405
You smell like Kakashi Sensei!

288
00:18:48,477 --> 00:18:49,535
The smell of an old guy!

289
00:18:51,180 --> 00:18:52,272
Why you!

290
00:18:52,414 --> 00:18:55,941
Hey! For the time being,
let's try undoing the Jutsu.

291
00:18:56,418 --> 00:18:58,909
If we do that,
only the two will remain... so...

292
00:18:59,221 --> 00:19:00,848
You should've realized that sooner,
you idiot!

293
00:19:01,156 --> 00:19:04,125
You're me, you idiot!
Just undo the Jutsu!

294
00:19:12,868 --> 00:19:13,857
<i>Naruto...</i>

295
00:19:14,436 --> 00:19:15,425
<i>You're embarrassing to watch...</i>

296
00:19:16,105 --> 00:19:18,699
<i>That was the Substitution Jutsu,</i>
<i>you fool.</i>

297
00:19:19,375 --> 00:19:22,367
<i>Essentially, it's a skill used</i>
<i>to quickly switch one's own body</i>

298
00:19:22,444 --> 00:19:24,435
<i>with an object or animal.</i>

299
00:19:24,847 --> 00:19:27,975
<i>This makes your enemy think</i>
<i>you're being attacked,</i>

300
00:19:28,484 --> 00:19:30,145
<i>but then you strike during</i>
<i>their unguarded moment.</i>

301
00:19:30,986 --> 00:19:35,252
<i>After letting himself get caught</i>
<i>by the real Naruto,</i>

302
00:19:35,324 --> 00:19:39,055
<i>the Jonin fool switched bodies</i>
<i>with one of the clone Narutos.</i>

303
00:19:39,695 --> 00:19:41,754
<i>Not only did he make Naruto</i>
<i>think he'd been nailed...</i>

304
00:19:42,097 --> 00:19:44,691
<i>he used Naruto's own attack on him.</i>

305
00:19:51,507 --> 00:19:52,337
<i>A bell?!</i>

306
00:19:53,809 --> 00:19:55,674
You really must have been in a hurry.

307
00:19:55,978 --> 00:19:57,411
You've dropped a bell!

308
00:20:02,284 --> 00:20:04,149
What the heck is this?!

309
00:20:06,789 --> 00:20:08,757
<i>Of course it's a trap...</i>

310
00:20:09,291 --> 00:20:12,055
H-H-Hey!

311
00:20:12,594 --> 00:20:17,998
<i>That jonin doesn't lower his guard</i>
<i>even when he's fighting Naruto.</i>

312
00:20:18,467 --> 00:20:20,230
The bell!

313
00:20:24,873 --> 00:20:26,864
You have to think when using Jutsu.

314
00:20:27,810 --> 00:20:30,005
They can be used against you.

315
00:20:31,880 --> 00:20:32,778
Also...

316
00:20:34,116 --> 00:20:37,381
...don't get caught in
an obvious trap, you fool.

317
00:20:39,888 --> 00:20:42,083
A Ninja must see
through deception!

318
00:20:42,391 --> 00:20:45,087
I know that, I say!

319
00:20:45,627 --> 00:20:48,118
You know, I'm telling you
because you <i>don't</i> get it.

320
00:20:48,197 --> 00:20:49,164
Listen up!

321
00:20:50,799 --> 00:20:53,427
Your movements are wasteful.

322
00:20:54,236 --> 00:20:55,100
<i>Now!</i>

323
00:20:59,041 --> 00:21:00,508
<i>He finally dropped his guard!</i>

324
00:21:01,176 --> 00:21:02,234
You're so...

325
00:21:06,415 --> 00:21:07,507
No way!

326
00:21:08,050 --> 00:21:09,210
You jerk Sasuke!

327
00:21:09,284 --> 00:21:10,774
You're overdoing it!

328
00:22:52,763 --> 00:22:53,627
Damn it!

329
00:22:53,797 --> 00:22:56,425
At this rate, there's no way
I can beat Kakashi Sensei.

330
00:22:56,633 --> 00:22:57,759
But if I don't take the bell...

331
00:22:57,835 --> 00:22:58,597
I won't get lunch...

332
00:22:58,669 --> 00:23:00,864
No... I'll fail the test!

333
00:23:01,138 --> 00:23:03,971
He says a Ninja must see
through deception,

334
00:23:04,041 --> 00:23:05,906
but I have no idea what that means.

335
00:23:06,176 --> 00:23:08,041
How in the world can I take
the bell back

336
00:23:08,112 --> 00:23:10,171
from Kakashi Sensei?!

337
00:23:11,315 --> 00:23:14,113
Next episode:
"You Failed! Kakashi's Final Decision"

338
00:23:14,184 --> 00:23:16,778
Don't miss my outstanding performance!
